body: "GH-612. --acceptance-criteria/--ac replaces the whole value; repeatable only within one invocation (joins with '; ' per pm-b84u). Across calls/branches, two agents each adding a criterion clobber the base and conflict on the single acceptance_criteria line. Fix: --add-ac/--remove-ac individual-criterion operations (tag-API parity), replace semantics unchanged for --ac; disjoint additions merge cleanly across branches (pm-m3nl scalar-line caveat applies)."
